sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as pureflow-cli
    participant Format as workflow-format
    participant Graph as workflow graph
    participant Engine as engine
    participant Runtime as runtime
    participant Node as node executor
    participant Meta as metadata JSONL

    User->>CLI: run workflow
    CLI->>Format: parse document
    Format->>Graph: build validated graph
    CLI->>Engine: start run
    Engine->>Runtime: schedule nodes
    Runtime->>Node: execute node
    Node-->>Runtime: packets or error
    Runtime->>Meta: emit records
    Engine-->>CLI: run summary
    CLI-->>User: status
